Description: Ciel has earned a seat at the Midnight Tea Party, where he will finally get a look at Weston’s enigmatic headmaster.
Title: BLACK BUTLER, VOL. 17
Author: Yana Toboso

Description: At the Death Weapon Meister Academy, Tsugumi Harudori joins the N.O.T. (Normally Overcome Target) class so she can gain better control of her powers and defend her friends.
Title: SOUL EATER NOT!, VOL. 3
Author: Atsushi Ohkubo

Description: Staz is no closer to restoring Fuyumi to her human body and now, he has to deal with his father, who has been resurrected by Braz.
Title: BLOOD LAD, VOL. 5
Author: Yuuki Kodama

Description: Maka stretches her soul perception ability to the limit so she can find Crona anywhere on the planet. But will she be able to reach Crona before Shinigami?
Title: SOUL EATER, VOL. 21
Author: Atsushi Ohkubo

Description: Is this the end of humanity? It sure looks that way when what is left of mankind must go into hiding to escape the giant humanoids known as the Titans.
Title: ATTACK ON TITAN, VOL. 1
Author: Hajime Isayama

Description: The ninja war rages on and Naruto is joined by his father in the effort to defeat Obito and Madara.
Title: NARUTO, VOL. 66
Author: Masashi Kishimoto

Description: In this final volume, Himari goes on a rampage and only Yuto can stop her!
Title: OMAMORI HIMARI, VOL. 12
Author: Milan Matra

Description: Tomoko Kuroki comes to a harsh realization when she begins high school: she’s horribly unpopular!
Title: NO MATTER HOW I LOOK AT IT, IT'S YOU GUYS' FAULT I'M NOT POPULAR!, VOL. 4
Author: Nico Tanigawa

Description: Mankind has gone into hiding to escape the giant humanoids known as the Titans. In this volume, what happens when a human boy becomes a Titan?
Title: ATTACK ON TITAN, VOL. 3
Author: Hajime Isayama

Description: The origins of the Survey Corps leaders Levi and Erwin are told in this spin–off series.
Title: ATTACK ON TITAN: NO REGRETS, VOL. 1
Author: Gun Snark, Hikaru Suruga and Hajime Isayama
Contributor: by Gun Snark, Hikaru Suruga and Hajime Isayama
